# Boolean and operators

## Boolean values

```py
True
False
type(True) # <class 'bool'>
```

## Comparison operators

```py
1 > 2 # False
1 < 2 # True
1 == 2 # False
1 != 2 # True
1 >= 2 # False
1 <= 2 # True
```

## Logical operators

```py
1 > 2 and 2 > 3 # False
1 < 2 and 2 < 3 # True
1 > 2 or 2 > 3 # False
1 < 2 or 2 > 3 # True
```
